metadata.name: Doors to parallel universes"
metadata.description: When I first came to know about space and how big the universe is it blowed my mind .not only that we have multiverse too so I always used to wonder how all those ancient civilizations made all those marvelous structure some say aliens helped us built that . if its true than how they used to travel cause space travelling takes a lot of time . but there are theories that they used to travel through portals wich made it easy to come and go and I believe that .
